    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wondered how the world of Trailmakers was built? Join us on a visual voyage from the genesis of the game and into our newest campaign by the pages of our art book &quot;The Art of Trailmakers&quot;. Throughout the book, we will explore environments, animals, characters and blocks, and even show the roads not taken - hitherto unseen art and concepts of critters and cosmoses. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How do I access artbooks on Steam?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To locate the artbook on your computer after the purchase, find the game in your Steam Library and click &quot;Browse local files&quot; in the &quot;Manage&quot; dropdown menu.</p>",
